short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save, Convert, Copy, and View SVGs from the internet.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"SVG Plus" helps you download SVGs like any other image on the internet.

You can save SVG as an SVG file or convert and save it as a PNG / JPEG file.
You can also Open individual SVG in a new tab or copy SVG text in your clipboard.
